<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Northlane | Backend Operations for Creators & Founders</title>
<meta name="description" content="Northlane handles the editing, design, scheduling, and posting, so your only job is showing up and hitting record.">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/favicon.png">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="assets/favicon.png">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg-primary:#0A0D14;
    --bg-secondary:#12151F;
    --bg-elevated:#1A1F2E;
    --border:#232838;
    --blue:#2952E3;
    --blue-deep:#1B3BB8;
    --blue-glow:#4C7CFF;
    --navy:#0F1A3D;
    --text-primary:#F5F6FA;
    --text-secondary:#9BA3B4;
    --success:#3DDC97;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:var(--bg-primary);
    color:var(--text-primary);
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
    font-size:16px;
    line-height:1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  h1,h2,h3,.display{
    font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;
    font-weight:700;
    letter-spacing:-0.015em;
    line-height:1.08;
  }
  p{color:var(--text-secondary);}
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
  img,svg{display:block;max-width:100%;}
  .container{
    max-width:1160px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:0 24px;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:13px;
    letter-spacing:0.12em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--blue-glow);
    margin-bottom:18px;
    display:block;
  }
  section{
    padding:120px 0;
  }
  .bg-secondary{background:var(--bg-secondary);}

  /* ---------- Buttons ---------- */
  .btn{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:8px;
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
    font-weight:600;
    font-size:15px;
    padding:14px 28px;
    border-radius:8px;
    cursor:pointer;
    border:none;
    transition:transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease, background .25s ease, border-color .25s ease;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .btn-primary{
    background:var(--blue);
    color:#fff;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{
    background:var(--blue-deep);
    box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(41,82,227,.35);
    transform:translateY(-2px);
  }
  .btn-ghost{
    background:transparent;
    color:var(--blue-glow);
    border:1.5px solid var(--blue);
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover{
    background:rgba(41,82,227,.1);
    border-color:var(--blue-glow);
  }
  .btn-small{
    padding:10px 20px;
    font-size:14px;
  }

  /* ---------- Nav ---------- */
  header{
    position:fixed;
    top:0; left:0; right:0;
    z-index:100;
    padding:22px 0;
    background:transparent;
    border-bottom:1px solid transparent;
    transition:background .3s ease, border-color .3s ease, padding .3s ease;
  }
  header.solid{
    background:rgba(10,13,20,.92);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    padding:16px 0;
  }
  nav{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
  }
  .logo{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:19px;
    letter-spacing:0.06em;
  }
  .logo-mark{
    width:28px;
    height:28px;
    object-fit:contain;
    display:block;
    flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .nav-links{
    display:flex;
    gap:36px;
    list-style:none;
  }
  .nav-links a{
    font-size:14.5px;
    font-weight:500;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
    transition:color .2s ease;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text-primary);}
  .nav-toggle{
    display:none;
    background:none;
    border:none;
    color:var(--text-primary);
    font-size:22px;
    cursor:pointer;
  }

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero{
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    position:relative;
    padding-top:120px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(41,82,227,.16), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--bg-primary) 65%);
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    inset:0;
    background-image:url('assets/nav-mark.png');
    background-repeat:no-repeat;
    background-position:center 38%;
    background-size:640px;
    opacity:.16;
    mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 38%, black 0%, black 35%, transparent 72%);
    -webkit-mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 38%, black 0%, black 35%, transparent 72%);
  }
  .hero-inner{
    position:relative;
    max-width:780px;
    margin:0 auto;
    text-align:center;
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:68px;
    margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  .hero h1 .accent{
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue-glow),var(--blue));
    -webkit-background-clip:text;
    background-clip:text;
    color:transparent;
  }
  .hero p.sub{
    font-size:19px;
    max-width:600px;
    margin:0 auto 40px;
  }
  .hero-ctas{
    display:flex;
    gap:16px;
    justify-content:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    margin-bottom:28px;
  }
  .hero-note{
    font-size:13.5px;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
    opacity:.85;
  }

  /* ---------- Fade up ---------- */
  .fade-up{
    opacity:0;
    transform:translateY(24px);
    transition:opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease;
  }
  .fade-up.in-view{
    opacity:1;
    transform:translateY(0);
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    .fade-up{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none;}
  }

  /* ---------- Section headers ---------- */
  .section-head{
    max-width:640px;
    margin:0 auto 64px;
    text-align:center;
  }
  .section-head h2{
    font-size:42px;
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .section-head p{
    font-size:17px;
  }

  /* ---------- Problem / Solution ---------- */
  .split{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr;
    gap:0;
    align-items:stretch;
  }
  .split-col{
    padding:44px;
  }
  .split-col.problem{
    background:var(--bg-primary);
  }
  .split-col.solution{
    background:var(--bg-elevated);
    border-radius:16px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .split-divider{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    width:56px;
    color:var(--blue);
    font-size:22px;
  }
  .split-label{
    font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:15px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:.06em;
    margin-bottom:24px;
    display:block;
  }
  .split-col.problem .split-label{color:var(--text-secondary);}
  .split-col.solution .split-label{color:var(--blue-glow);}
  .split-list{
    list-style:none;
  }
  .split-list li{
    display:flex;
    gap:14px;
    padding:14px 0;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    font-size:15.5px;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .split-list li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .split-list .dot{
    flex-shrink:0;
    width:7px;height:7px;
    border-radius:50%;
    margin-top:8px;
  }
  .problem .dot{background:#4A4F5E;}
  .solution .dot{background:var(--success);}
  .solution li{color:var(--text-primary);}

  /* ---------- Services ---------- */
  .cards{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
    gap:24px;
  }
  .card{
    background:var(--bg-elevated);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:36px 30px;
    transition:transform .3s ease, border-color .3s ease, box-shadow .3s ease;
  }
  .card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-6px);
    border-color:var(--blue);
    box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
  }
  .card-icon{
    width:44px;height:44px;
    border-radius:10px;
    background:rgba(41,82,227,.14);
    color:var(--blue-glow);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    margin-bottom:22px;
  }
  .card h3{
    font-size:20px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  .card .one-liner{
    font-size:14.5px;
    margin-bottom:22px;
  }
  .card ul{
    list-style:none;
  }
  .card ul li{
    display:flex;
    gap:10px;
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
    padding:8px 0;
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .card ul li:first-child{border-top:none;}
  .card ul li svg{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;color:var(--success);}

  /* ---------- How it works ---------- */
  .steps{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
    gap:40px;
    position:relative;
  }
  .steps::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    top:34px;
    left:8%;
    right:8%;
    height:1px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue), var(--blue), transparent);
    opacity:.5;
  }
  .step{
    position:relative;
    text-align:left;
  }
  .step-num{
    font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;
    font-weight:800;
    font-size:56px;
    color:var(--blue);
    margin-bottom:18px;
    position:relative;
    background:var(--bg-primary);
    display:inline-block;
    padding-right:18px;
  }
  .step h3{
    font-size:19px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  .step p{font-size:15px;}

  /* ---------- Founder ---------- */
  .founder{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:340px 1fr;
    gap:64px;
    align-items:start;
  }
  .founder-frame{
    width:100%;
    aspect-ratio:1/1;
    border-radius:20px;
    border:1px solid var(--blue);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(76,124,255,.35), transparent 55%),
      var(--bg-elevated);
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .founder-frame img{
    position:absolute;
    inset:0;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    object-fit:cover;
  }
  .founder-frame .mono{
    font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;
    font-weight:800;
    font-size:96px;
    color:var(--blue-glow);
    opacity:.9;
  }
  .founder-label{
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight:600;
    letter-spacing:.12em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--blue-glow);
    display:block;
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .founder-letter p{
    font-size:16.5px;
    color:#C7CCDA;
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .founder-sign{
    color:var(--text-primary);
    font-weight:600;
    margin-top:8px;
  }

  /* ---------- Final CTA ---------- */
  .final-cta{
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, rgba(41,82,227,.18), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary), #05060a);
    text-align:center;
  }
  .final-cta h2{
    font-size:48px;
    max-width:680px;
    margin:0 auto 20px;
  }
  .final-cta > .container > p{
    max-width:520px;
    margin:0 auto 40px;
    font-size:17px;
  }
  .contact-block{
    margin-top:56px;
    display:flex;
    gap:40px;
    justify-content:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .contact-block strong{
    display:block;
    color:var(--text-primary);
    font-size:13px;
    letter-spacing:.06em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin-bottom:6px;
    font-weight:600;
  }
  .contact-block a{
    color:var(--text-secondary);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    transition:color .2s ease, border-color .2s ease;
  }
  .contact-block a:hover{
    color:var(--blue-glow);
    border-color:var(--blue-glow);
  }

  .lead-form{
    max-width:480px;
    margin:0 auto;
    background:var(--bg-elevated);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:32px;
    text-align:left;
  }
  .lead-form label{
    display:block;
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight:600;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom:8px;
  }
  .field{margin-bottom:18px;}
  .lead-form input,
  .lead-form select{
    width:100%;
    background:var(--bg-primary);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:8px;
    padding:12px 14px;
    color:var(--text-primary);
    font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
    font-size:14.5px;
  }
  .lead-form input:focus,
  .lead-form select:focus{
    outline:none;
    border-color:var(--blue);
  }
  .lead-form button{width:100%;margin-top:6px;}
  .form-success{
    display:none;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px 0;
    color:var(--success);
    font-weight:600;
  }
  .form-success.show{display:block;}
  .lead-form.submitted form{display:none;}

  /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
  footer{
    background:var(--bg-secondary);
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    padding:56px 0 40px;
  }
  .footer-inner{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:flex-end;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:24px;
  }
  .footer-left{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:flex-start;
    gap:10px;
  }
  .footer-tagline{
    font-size:14px;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
    max-width:280px;
  }
  .footer-right{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:flex-end;
    gap:12px;
  }
  .footer-social{
    display:flex;
    gap:12px;
  }
  .footer-social a{
    width:32px;height:32px;
    border-radius:50%;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
    transition:border-color .2s ease, color .2s ease;
  }
  .footer-social a:hover{border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--blue-glow);}
  .footer-copy{
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--text-secondary);
  }

  /* ---------- Mobile sticky CTA ---------- */
  .sticky-cta{
    position:fixed;
    bottom:0;left:0;right:0;
    z-index:90;
    padding:14px 20px;
    background:rgba(10,13,20,.95);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    display:none;
    transform:translateY(100%);
    transition:transform .3s ease;
  }
  .sticky-cta.show{transform:translateY(0);}
  .sticky-cta .btn{width:100%;}

  /* ---------- Responsive ---------- */
  @media (max-width:900px){
    .hero::before{background-size:380px;background-position:center 32%;}
    .hero h1{font-size:44px;}
    .split{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .split-divider{display:none;}
    .split-col.problem{padding:36px 8px;}
    .split-col.solution{padding:36px 24px;margin-top:8px;}
    .cards{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .steps{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:48px;}
    .steps::before{display:none;}
    .founder{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:36px;}
    .founder-frame{max-width:280px;}
    .final-cta h2{font-size:34px;}
    .footer-inner{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;}
    .footer-right{align-items:flex-start;}
    .nav-links{
      position:fixed;
      top:0;right:0;
      height:100vh;
      width:240px;
      background:var(--bg-secondary);
      border-left:1px solid var(--border);
      flex-direction:column;
      padding:100px 32px;
      gap:28px;
      transform:translateX(100%);
      transition:transform .3s ease;
    }
    .nav-links.open{transform:translateX(0);}
    .nav-toggle{display:block;}
    .nav-cta{display:none;}
    .sticky-cta{display:block;}
    section{padding:80px 0;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header id="siteHeader">
  <div class="container">
    <nav>
      <a href="#top" class="logo"><img src="assets/nav-mark.png" alt="" class="logo-mark">NORTHLANE</a>
      <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a></li>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-small nav-cta">Book a Discovery Call</a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">☰</button>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="top">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">Backend Operations for Creators & Founders</span>
      <h1>You Create. We Handle <span class="accent">Everything Else.</span></h1>
      <p class="sub">Northlane handles the editing, design, scheduling, and posting, so your only job is showing up and hitting record.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Discovery Call</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-note">Trusted by creators and founders who'd rather grow than manage a task list.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem / Solution -->
  <section id="about" class="bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head fade-up">
        <h2>Creating Is the Job. Managing Everything Around It Isn't.</h2>
        <p>Every hour you spend editing, resizing, scheduling, or formatting is an hour you're not spending on the thing that actually grows your audience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="split fade-up">
        <div class="split-col problem">
          <span class="split-label">Running It Yourself</span>
          <ul class="split-list">
            <li><span class="dot"></span>Editing long-form footage down at 11pm because it's the only time you have</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>Second-guessing your own thumbnail design instead of your next video idea</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>Manually resizing and reposting the same clip six different ways for six platforms</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>Losing momentum between uploads because scheduling falls through the cracks</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>Burnout creeping in, until content feels like a chore instead of the thing you love</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="split-divider">→</div>
        <div class="split-col solution">
          <span class="split-label">Handing It to Northlane</span>
          <ul class="split-list">
            <li><span class="dot"></span>You record. We edit, package, and optimize it, every single time</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>A dedicated team building thumbnails and hooks that are built to convert</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>One upload becomes a full week of content across every platform, automatically</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>A consistent publishing calendar that never depends on your energy that day</li>
            <li><span class="dot"></span>More time, more output, and content that still sounds and looks like you</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head fade-up">
        <h2>What We Take Off Your Plate</h2>
        <p>Three areas, fully managed. Pick one, or hand us all of it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards fade-up">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M21 8.5c0-2-1.5-3.6-3.5-3.8-3.6-.4-7.4-.4-11 0C4.5 4.9 3 6.5 3 8.5v7c0 2 1.5 3.6 3.5 3.8 3.6.4 7.4.4 11 0 2-.2 3.5-1.8 3.5-3.8v-7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M10 9.5l5 2.5-5 2.5v-5z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>YouTube Operations</h3>
          <p class="one-liner">We manage your whole channel, from raw footage to published upload.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Custom thumbnail design built to drive clicks</li>
            <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Channel analytics tracked and reported monthly</li>
            <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Long-form editing and repurposing</li>
            <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Full upload scheduling and on-page SEO</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
